CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `collection` (`id` smallint(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`level` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,`parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`amount_bank` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT 0.0,`add_date` datetime DEFAULT current_timestamp(),PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `division` (`id` smallint(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`level` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,`title` char(100) DEFAULT NULL,`name` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`assist` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`is_document` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `guides` (`id` mediumint(7) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`name` varchar(350) NOT NULL,`price` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT 0.0,`share` float DEFAULT 0,`add_date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `multi_accounts` (`id` smallint(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`slot` char(20) NOT NULL,`user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `province` (`id` tinyint(2) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`name` char(70) NOT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `region` (`id` smallint(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`province_id` tinyint(2) NOT NULL,`name` char(255) NOT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `service` (`id` smallint(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`user_level` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,`division_id` smallint(5) DEFAULT NULL,`code` char(30) DEFAULT NULL,`name` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,`price` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT NULL,`type` smallint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `sessions` (`session_id` char(255) NOT NULL,`self_id` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,`self_ip` char(15) DEFAULT NULL,`self_login` char(100) DEFAULT NULL,`self_render` char(200) DEFAULT NULL,`self_agent` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,`last_update` datetime DEFAULT current_timestamp(),`first_login` datetime DEFAULT current_timestamp(),PRIMARY KEY (`session_id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `sidebar` (`id` tinyint(3) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`level` smallint(2) DEFAULT NULL,`sort` tinyint(2) DEFAULT NULL,`is_parent` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`module` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`route` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`icon` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`name` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`is_active` varchar(700) DEFAULT NULL,`is_division` char(3) DEFAULT NULL,`script` text DEFAULT NULL,`script_item` tinytext DEFAULT NULL,`badge_class` char(100) DEFAULT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `users` (`id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`username` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,`password` char(70) DEFAULT NULL,`is_active` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`first_name` char(30) DEFAULT NULL,`last_name` char(30) DEFAULT NULL,`father_name` char(30) DEFAULT NULL,`dateBith` date DEFAULT NULL,`region` char(255) DEFAULT NULL,`passport_seria` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`passport_pin_fl` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`placeWork` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,`position` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,`numberPhone` char(255) DEFAULT NULL,`residenceAddress` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,`registrationAddress` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,`gender` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`user_level` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,`division_id` smallint(5) DEFAULT NULL,`status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT 1,`share` float DEFAULT 0,`resident` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`room` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL,`token_telegramm` char(250) DEFAULT NULL,`pacs_login` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`pacs_password` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`add_date` datetime(6) DEFAULT current_timestamp(6),PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `visit` (`id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,`grant_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`route_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`assist_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`division_id` smallint(5) DEFAULT NULL,`service_id` smallint(5) DEFAULT NULL,`bed_id` smallint(5) DEFAULT NULL,`direction` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT 0,`diagnostic` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`laboratory` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`physio` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`manipulation` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`guide_id` mediumint(7) DEFAULT NULL,`complaint` varchar(700) DEFAULT NULL,`failure` char(200) DEFAULT NULL,`report_title` char(200) DEFAULT NULL,`report` text DEFAULT NULL,`add_date` datetime DEFAULT current_timestamp(),`accept_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,`priced_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,`discharge_date` date DEFAULT NULL,`completed` datetime DEFAULT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `visit_price` (`id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`visit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`pricer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`operation_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`price_cash` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT 0.0,`price_card` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT 0.0,`price_transfer` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT 0.0,`sale` float DEFAULT 0,`status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,`item_type` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,`item_id` int(11) NOT NULL,`item_cost` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT 0.0,`item_name` varchar(500) NOT NULL,`price_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,`add_date` datetime DEFAULT current_timestamp(),PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
